---
title: Herby Spiced Chicken with Buttery Curry Sauce and Fluffy Rice
description: We love a good Chicken with Curry Sauce and Rice and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/herby-spiced-chicken-c21b3250-c1871bb2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/herby-spiced-chicken-5d03a4226629a50013632e07-67e31c58.pdf
